works.description:
Album cover image for Van Halen, 1984  
Album of a young angel smoking a cigarette sitting behind a marble table. 
 
The angel has blond hair combed up and forward.  There are 2 packs of  
cigarettes sitting on the table.  Although this illustration has been put 

in a horizontal format as opposed to verticle, it is my illustration.
